text: Saint-Paterne is a former commune. It is found in the region Pays de la Loire in the Sarthe department in the west of France. On 1 January 2017, it was merged into the new commune of Saint-Paterne - Le Chevain.Arrêté préfectoral 28 September 2016 == References == Category:Former communes in Sarthe
title: Saint-Paterne
